Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:28.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}牢笼里多么的安全　舒适而没有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:33.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘却了创造　这里将被光明抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来倾吐希望　让不满爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}吹响革新的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我要全力攀登　再不让他人企及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:48.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突破血雨腥风　让他们全都辟易
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:53.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绝对的控制　将令我咽喉干渴无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:58.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却无法夺去我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让一切感官嘶吼激昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:05.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不把炽热的情感寄托在音符中唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:11.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}怎会令心脏热血滚烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:16.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:20.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We must be the change we wish to see
