Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}响彻青天的霹雳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}闪光掠过的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:02.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无声无息　阴影迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:06.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}尔虞我诈　逐渐失去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:09.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}以眼还眼　互相争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:13.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}逐渐磨损本该保护的正以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:17.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}也绝对不会赢得任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:20.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}在笼中仰望到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}雨过天晴眩目的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:27.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}不甘永远被囚禁于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}哪怕要让我舍弃过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:34.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}要遵从之物仅有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}本能激发着无穷动力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:41.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无论如何都要做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:45.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}因为改变对我是难题
